name: the myth dies of natural causes outside of a best buy in northern indiana
description: die with the most likes x clokdhd collaboration. there is a best buy in northern indiana. where most people die. a retail outlet. that pulverizes flesh. into used DVDs. and dreams into the skid marked rug underneath the nintendo 64 demo stand. the only place in the world where you can snort ketamine off of a DELL fax machine and peruse blu ray lego pornography behind a beaded promotional curtain from Austin Powers Goldmember. die as the myth does. die buying a mountain dew code red and the latest NOW that's what I call music album. join the rest of those buried in caskets made from itunes gift cards. achieve salvation in the dated technology.
